description:
What is intercessory prayer? How is intercessory prayer different than prayers of petition on behalf of others? Why is intercessory prayer essential for those who’ve turned away from God? 

Through Scriptures, Bible stories, and real-life examples, Pastor Pavel Goia explores the subject of intercessory prayer. What are the elements of effective intercessory prayer? What should be the focus of intercessory prayer? How can you maintain your dedication to praying for someone over long periods of time when you don’t see results? 

Learn why intercessory prayer is essential for the salvation of those you pray for and for your personal relationship with God.
